Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Create a Linear Regression model using BLB (Bag of Little Bootstraps)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Razmig Zeitounian
Maintainer: Razmig Zeitounian <rzeitounian@ucdavis.edu>
Description: Estimate a Linear Model using BLB (Bag of Little Bootstraps).
    Can get values like coefficient, sigma, etc. from model with the option to parallelize computations.
    Parallelizing is only recommended for larger data.frame objects
